data.name: sqlInsertCommand1.CommandText
data.value: INSERT INTO [Train] ([Train_No], [Train_Name], [Train_Type], [No_of_FirstClassSeats], [No_of_SecondClassSeats], [No_of_ThirdClassSeats]) VALUES (@Train_No, @Train_Name, @Train_Type, @No_of_FirstClassSeats, @No_of_SecondClassSeats, @No_of_ThirdClassSeats); SELECT Train_No, Train_Name, Train_Type, No_of_FirstClassSeats, No_of_SecondClassSeats, No_of_ThirdClassSeats FROM Train WHERE (Train_No = @Train_No)

data.name: sqlUpdateCommand1.CommandText
data.value: UPDATE [Train] SET [Train_No] = @Train_No, [Train_Name] = @Train_Name, [Train_Type] = @Train_Type, [No_of_FirstClassSeats] = @No_of_FirstClassSeats, [No_of_SecondClassSeats] = @No_of_SecondClassSeats, [No_of_ThirdClassSeats] = @No_of_ThirdClassSeats WHERE (([Train_No] = @Original_Train_No) AND ([Train_Name] = @Original_Train_Name) AND ([Train_Type] = @Original_Train_Type) AND ([No_of_FirstClassSeats] = @Original_No_of_FirstClassSeats) AND ([No_of_SecondClassSeats] = @Original_No_of_SecondClassSeats) AND ([No_of_ThirdClassSeats] = @Original_No_of_ThirdClassSeats)); SELECT Train_No, Train_Name, Train_Type, No_of_FirstClassSeats, No_of_SecondClassSeats, No_of_ThirdClassSeats FROM Train WHERE (Train_No = @Train_No)
